FBIS4-45227 "jptdd023__l94071" JPRS-TDD-94-023-L JPRS Narcotics 25 May 1994 NEAR EAST & SOUTH ASIA LEBANON Security Personnel Seize Nearly One Ton of Hashish Bound for Security Personnel Seize Nearly One Ton of Hashish Bound for Italy NC2505183194 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 25 May 94 NC2505183194 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] Security personnel from the Counternarcotics Bureau raided al-Karantina locality near the Beirut port. They discovered about one ton of hashish packed in 79 cardboard boxes, each weighing 15 kg. The shipment was to be smuggled into Italy.
